  "remarks": "Member of the \"Parliament\" of the so-called \"Donetsk People's Republic\" and Chairman of the public association Union of veterans of the Donbass Berkut and a member of the public movement \"Free Donbass\". Stood as a candidate in the so-called \"elections\" of 2 Nov 2014 to the post of the Head of the so-called \"Donetsk People's Republic\". These elections were in breach of Ukrainian law and therefore illegal.",
